"ensuring they are started and stopped in the right order."
msgstr ""
"Run the GNU Shepherd as PID 1---i.e., the operating system's first\n"
"process.  The Shepherd takes care of managing services such as daemons by\n"
"ensuring they are started and stopped in the right order."

